1: Speech to text input
    Speech to text engine such as OpenAI Whisper or Vosk
    Feeds the text into an AI

2: AI - Text to decision 
    Local AI model (Ollama)
    AI produces a text output

3: Command Engine (translates AI output into real actions)
    Open apps
    Control music
    Search the web

4: Text to Speech
    Any verbal output from the AI is turned into a speech output

5: System Integration (lets GabbO control Windows)
    OS/subprocess - open apps
    pyautogui - control mouse % keyboard
    webbrowser - open websites 